unwound.title: Pizza to the Polls will send you free pizza while you wait to vote
unwound.description: Waiting in line to vote can happen around dinner time, so why go hungry? Pizza to the Polls is offering to deliver pizza to people waiting in long lines at polling places — for free! The organization is asking people to report long lines at the polls by sending them an address and a picture. Then they'll deliver the pizza.
